summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Blocks 3 and 4, Chilberg's Addition, Block 473, Seattle Tide Lands, Extension No. 1, and Lots 11 and 12, Block 18, Lake Union Second Addition, with respect to Use District, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto a new section numbered 2-35.
